      <h2 id="headline" class="article-full-headline">Swarf</h2>
      <p id="byline" class="article-full-byline">ERICA FUNKHOUSER</p>
      <div>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">If you have seen</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">the fine metallic filings</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">flying onto the fellow</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">who crimps copper</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">into flashing and fashions</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">pivot hinges from brass,</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">you have seen it.</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">This is not the late</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">Bronze Age.</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">There are no palace</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">economies, only</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">the economy of one man</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">milling metal to earn</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">the flimsy dollars</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">that keep him fed.</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">When you knock on his door</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">he quiets the grindstone</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">raises his polycarbonate visor</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">and greets you swathed</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">in a swarm of gold—</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">not war gold or altar gold</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">but the metalsmith’s</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">hard-won residue:</p>
         <p xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="article-full-body">swarf.</p>
